Okweyongera kw'obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe (COVID-19) mu European Union/European Economic Area ne mu United Kingdom, okuva nga 1 January okutuuka nga 15 March 2020
Okubuuka kw'endwadde ya coronavirus (COVID-19) kulaga embeera y'emu mu mawanga agali mu European Union/European Economic Area ne United Kingdom nga kikakasa nti, wadde nga kiri mu mbeera ya njawulo okusinziira ku ggwanga, ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kikulaakulana mangu mu mawanga gonna.
Okusinziira ku bumanyirivu obuvudde mu Italy, ensi, amalwaliro n'ebitongole by'obujjanjabi obwa nnamaddala birina okwongera okwetegekera okw'amaanyi okw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abajja okwetaaga obujjanjabi, n'okusingira ddala obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi.
Nga 31 Ddesemba 2019, omuwendo gw'abantu abaalina obulwadde bw'omusujja gw'amabeere nga tebamanyiddwa lwaki baalabika mu Wuhan, mu ssaza lya Hubei, China.
Nga 9 January 2020, China Center for Disease Control and Prevention yalangirira nti ekirwadde kino kyava ku coronavirus empya kati eyitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obuva mu bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwatuumibwa obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Obujulizi obwazuulibwa okwetoloola ennaku zino bulaga nti abantu nga 80% abalina COVID-19 balina obulwadde obw'ekigero, kwe kugamba, obulwadde bw'ebitundu by'okussa omukka nga balina oba nga tebalina kirwadde kya puleesa, era abasinga obungi ku bano bawona.
Mu bantu 14 ku buli kikumi, COVID-19 ekulaakulana n'afuuka obulwadde obw'amaanyi obwetaaga okuteekebwa mu ddwaliro ng'ate abantu 6 ku buli kikumi be bafuna obulwadde obw'amaanyi obwetaaga okulabirirwa ennyo.
Okufa kw'abalwadde abakwatibwa COVID-19 mu ddwaliro kuli ku bitundu 4%.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, twekenneenya enkola y'okufuna COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga lya European Union/European Economic Area (EU/EEA) ne United Kingdom (UK) era ne tugigeraageranya n'ekyo eky'essaza lya Hubei, China.
Twegeraageranya n'omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK n'ogwa Italy mu 31 Jjanwali-15 Maaki 2020.
Ebitundu bya COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK
Oluvannyuma lwa China, COVID-19 yayongera okusaasaana mu bitundu ebirala era embeera y'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 mu nsi yonna mu kiseera kino egoberera eya ggwanga lino.
Nga 11 Ogwokusatu 2020, Omukulu w'Ekibiina ky'Eby'Obulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) yalangirira nti COVID-19 yali kawumpuli.
Mu magazini ya Eurosurveillance 2020, eya Maaki 5, Spiteri n'abalala baategeeza ku bantu abasooka okukakasibwa mu Bulaaya nga bafunye COVID-19 okusinziira ku ngeri WHO gy'etegeeramu abantu abafunye obulwadde.
Mu EU/EEA, abantu basatu abaasooka abakakasiddwa nti balina obulwadde buno baawulirwa France nga 24 Jjanwali 2020 mu bantu abaali bakomyewo okuva e Wuhan, mu ssaza ly'e Hubei, China.
Ku 15 Maaki 2020, abalwadde ba COVID-19 baalabikira mu mawanga gonna 30 aga EU/EEA ne United Kingdom (UK), era wakati wa 31 December 2019 n'olunaku olwo nga luzingirwamu, abalwadde 39,768 n'abafa 1,727 be baazuulibwa, nga 17,750 be baalabikira mu Italy mwokka ate 1,441 be baafa.
Okufuna omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa n'omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa abalina COVID-19
Ku European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa ne COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga mu nsi yonna, oguli mu nsimbi za gavumenti zokka nga Minisitule y'Ebyobulamu mu mawanga, ebitongole by'ebyobulamu mu mawanga n'ebitundu n'ekitongole ky'ensi yonna ekirwanyisa endwadde, bikyusibwamu buli lunaku ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'oku makya.
Ebirango bino byakozesebwa okwetegereza embeera ya COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne UK, era n'okugeraageranya n'eyo eri mu Italy.
Ng'ekitegeeza omuwendo gw'abantu abalina COVID-19 mu kiseera kino, twategera ennaku 14 ez'abantu abalina COVID-19, nga bwe tugoberera ekkubo lya COVID-19, mu buli nsi ya EU/EEA ne UK, wakati wa 1 Jjanwali ne 15 Maaki 2020.
Twayise era omuwendo gw'abantu abalabuddwa ku buli ggwanga nga 15 omwezi gwa March 2020 ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'oku makya nga gukwatagana n'ogwa Italy mu kiseera kya 31 omwezi gwa January okutuuka ku 15 omwezi gwa March 2020.
Enkola ya COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK
Enkula y'ebikolwa by'ennaku 14 eby'okubulira awamu eby'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK mu butonde by'ebiri bigoberera ebyo eby'e Hubei mu China (Figure 1).
Mu EU/EEA ne UK okutwalira awamu, obulwadde bwa COVID-19 bwatandika okweyongera ku Lwokubiri 21 ne bweyongera okukwata abantu ku Lwokubiri 28 2020 (Ebintu eby'Okwongera).
Kino ky'ekyasinze okuviirako omuwendo gw'abantu abaasangibwa n'obulwadde okuva e Italy okwongera okukula amangu, naye ate amawanga amalala gonna aga EU/EEA n'e UK galaga nti omuwendo gw'abantu abafuna COVID-19 gweyongedde (Ebintu eby'okweyongera).
Ekifaananyi 2 kiraga omuwendo gw'abantu abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK nga bwe bageraageranyizibwa n'abo abaali mu Italy mu kiseera ekya 31 Jjanwali-15 Maaki 2020.
Kiggumiza nti, nga 15 Ogwokusatu ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'ekiro, amawanga amalala 15 aga EU/EEA n'eggwanga lya UK baali bamaze okutegeeza omuwendo gw'abantu abafa ogwenkanankana n'ogwa Italy wiiki 3 ezaayita oba nga tezinnawera.
Ebyava mu kunoonyereza kwaffe biraga nti omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abalagiddwa gweyongera mangu mu EU/EEA ne UK.
Enkyukakyuka ezirabikako mu bungi bw'abantu abafuna COVID-19 ziraga nti ekirwadde kino kigenda mu maaso mu bwangu mu mawanga gonna.
Kino kikola wadde nga buli nsi eri mu mitendera egy'enjawulo, enjawulo mu ngeri y'okuddamu mu by'obulamu bw'abantu mu nsi yonna, era n'enjawulo mu ngeri omuntu gy'ategeerekamu mu nsi ez'enjawulo era n'enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okulonda abalwadde abalina okwekebezebwa okukakasa nti balina COVID-19, nga mw'otwalidde n'okwekebejjebwa okw'okudda mu maaso.
Ku ntandikwa ya March 2020, abasawo mu bitundu bya Italy eby'okwokebwa, baayogera ku mbeera mwe baali nga 10% ku balwadde ba COVID-19 beetaaga okujjanjabibwa mu ngeri ey'amaanyi era emikutu gy'amawulire ne gyogera nti amalwaliro n'ebitongole by'obujjanjabi mu bitundu ebyo byali bituuse ku ntikko yaabyo.
Ebikwata ku kukkiriza abantu abalina COVID-19 mu malwaliro ne/oba mu kitongole ekirabirira abantu ab'amaanyi mu kiseera kino biri ku ddaala lya EU/EEA ku bantu 6% bokka ate 1% ku bantu abafunye obulwadde (obubaka tebulabikiddwako).
Wabula, birina okukuŋŋaanyizibwa mu ngeri entegeke obulungi okusobola okujjuza obubaka obuliwo obukuumibwa nga bukwata ku muwendo gw'abantu abaweereddwa obulwadde n'abafudde.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 2010-11 kwalaga enjawulo ya maanyi mu kufunibwa kw'ebitanda mu ddwaaliro ery'amaanyi ne mu ddwaaliro erya wakati mu Bulaaya, okuva ku 29.2 mu Bugirimaani okutuuka ku bitanda 4.2 buli bantu 100,000 mu Portugal.
Kino kitegeeza nti ensi ziyinza okuba n'ebikozesebwa bingi oba bitono okusinga Italy (ebitanda 12.5 eby'okulabirira abalwadde mu 2010).
Enkola z'ekivvulu ekwata ku kukusa obujjanjabi bw'ekisawo, nga kuliko n'enkula ya buli nsi ya EU/EEA ne UK ey'omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abajjanjabibwa mu malwaliro nga balina &gt; akabi akali ku 90% ak'okusukka ku busobozi bw'ebisenge by'abasawo, ziweereddwa mu kuddamu okw'omukaaga okw'ebiteberezebwa ku COVID-19 mu bwangu okuva mu ECDC.
Okuva ng'ebirwadde kino bikwataganye mu bitundu ebimu mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK, era nga n'amalwaliro n'ebitongole by'abajjanjabi ab'amaanyi batera okuweereza abantu abali mu bitundu eby'enjawulo, obubaka obukwata ku birwadde n'ebitanda by'abajjanjabi ab'amaanyi bwetaaga okuteekebwa mu Nomenclature of Territorial Units for Statistics 2 (NUTS-2) level.
Ebyava mu Italy n'embeera eziriwo mu nsi endala biraga nti ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kigenda mu maaso mangu mu EU/EEA ne UK.
Ensi, amalwaliro n'ebitongole by'okulabirira abalwadde abawere birina okwetegekera embeera ey'okusaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu n'okweyongera kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, nga bwe kiri mu bitundu bya Italy ebirwadde.
Nga bwe kyalagiddwa mu kutegeka kw'obubonero bw'obulabe obw'amangu mu ECDC gye buvuddeko, enkola ey'amangu, ey'obunyiikivu era eya bonna nkulu nnyo mu kuwummula okusaasaana kwa SARS-COV-2, nga n'okudda mu maaso n'okukendeeza ku bubonero bw'obubonero, ng'okweyongera okw'amangu mu muwendo gw'emisango kuyinza obutaweesa basawo n'amalwaliro ebiseera ebimala okutegeera, okukkiriza n'okukyusa mu ngeri gye balwanyisaamu singa tebatambuzibwa mu budde.
Mu kuwunzika kw'obulabe obw'amangu era mulimu ennamba y'ebikolwa by'obulamu by'abantu eby'okumalawo obuzibu bw'obulwadde buno.
Waliwo ekiseera kitono ensi mwe zirina omukisa okwongera okwongera ku kaweefube w'okutangira SARS-CoV-2 okusaasaana n'okukendeeza ku bwetaavu ku by'obulamu.
Singa kino kilemererwa, kirabika nti enkola y'obujjanjabi mu nsi endala eza EU/EEA ejja kufuna omuwendo omungi gw'abalwadde abeetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi mu nnaku oba wiiki ezijja.
Obulwadde bwa Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), obwaleetebwa siriimu ey'amaanyi ey'okussa (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kati buzze butta abantu abasukka mu 3,000 era ne balwala abasukka 80,000 mu China ne mu nsi yonna, nga kiviiriddeko abantu okubonaabona.
Okufaananako akawuka ke akalala, SARS-CoV, akaaleeta SARS mu nkumi n'enkumi z'abantu mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 era ayinza okuva ku kasasiro era n'aleeta obubonero obufaanana okuyita mu nkola efaananako.
Kyokka, COVID-19 erina obuzibu n'obutafa bw'esinga SARS naye nga y'esinga okusasaanya era ekwata abantu abakulu okusinga abavubuka era n'abasajja okusinga abakazi.
Olw'omuwendo gw'ebitabo ebikubibwa ku bulwadde buno obugenda bweyongera, ekitundu kino kigezaako okuwaayo okwetegereza okw'ekiseera era okw'omunda ku nsonga eno ey'okunoonyereza eyeeyongera amangu.
Tujja kwogera ku by'ensibuko ebikwata ku bulwadde, ebireeta obulwadde, obuwuka, okuzuula, okujjanjaba, okulabula, n'okwewala obulwadde.
Wadde ebibuuzo bingi bikyetaaga eby'okuddamu, tusuubira nti okwetegereza kuno kujja kuyamba mu kutegeera n'okumalawo obulwadde buno obulabula.
Embaga ya Sseggulo nga January 25, 2020 efuuse ekijjukizo ekitabangawo era ekitajjukirwa eri Abachina bonna abalagirwa okusigala mu nnyumba okumala ennaku zonna ez'ekisiibo era n'okumala wiiki eziwera oluvannyuma olw'okusaasaana kw'obulwadde obuyitibwa 'novel viral disease'.
Akasimu kano kakwatagana nnyo ne coronavirus (CoV) eyaleeta ekirwadde ekikosa ennyo eky'okussa essimu (SARS) mu 2003; n'olwekyo, Ekibiina ky'Eby'Obulamu mu Nsi Yonna (WHO) kyakiyita SARS-CoV-2 nga Febwali 11, 2020, era obulwadde obugirimu ne buyitibwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Obulwadde buno bwatandikira mu Wuhan, China, era ne busaasaana mangu mu ggwanga lyonna era ne mu bitundu ebirala 50 okwetooloola ensi yonna.
Okutuuka nga Maaki 2, 2020, akawuka kano kaviiriddeko abantu abasukka mu 80,000 okukakasibwa nti balina COVID-19, ng'abalwadde abasukka mu 40,000 bawonye era n'abasukka mu 3,000 be baafa.
WHO erabula nti COVID-19 ye 'mulabe w'abantu omukulu' era ayinza okuba ow'amaanyi okusinga obutujju.
Okusinziira ku PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu myezi ebiri gyokka, ebitabo ebisoba mu 200 bifulumiziddwa ku COVID-19 nga mwemuli obuwuka obwa COVID-19, obulwadde, obuzaale, obujjanjabi, n'obujjanjabi okuva alipoota esooka ku Jjanwali 7, 2020 eyamanya enkula ya akawuka akaawulwa okuva mu balwadde abangi.
Okunoonyereza kuno kugezaako okuwunzika enkulaakulana y'ebinoonyereza mu kitundu kino ekippya era ekyeyongera okukulaakulana amangu.
Buli lwe kibeera kisoboka, tujja kugezaako okugeraageranya COVID-19 ku SARS n'obulwadde obulala obuleetebwa CoV, Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, ekirwadde ekyayaka mu 2012).
Era tujja kwogera ku ebyo bye tuyize ku ngeri y'okwewalamu obulwadde n'engeri gye busobola okukeberebwamu awamu n'ebibuuzo ebirala ebikulu.
CoVs zibadde zitwalibwa ng'endala ezitafa eri abantu, nga zireeta kumpi 15% ku ssennyiga 4.
Kyokka, mu kyasa kino, tusisinkanye CoVs ez'obubulwadde obw'amaanyi mu bantu emirundi ebiri, nga SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, ezaaleetawo obulwadde obwasooka mu China mu 2003 ne Saudi Arabia mu 2012, era amangu ddala ne zibuna mu nsi endala nnyingi nga zirina obulwadde obw'entiisa n'okufa.
N'olwekyo, COVID-19 y'emu kati ye CoV ey'okusatu eyabalukawo mu byafaayo by'abantu.
Nga bwe kiragiddwa mu kifaananyi. Ekifaananyi.1,1, ebibinja by'omusaayi gw'amawuggwe ebirina ensibuko emanyiddwa tebyasooka kutegeezebwa okuva e Wuhan nga Ddesemba 31, 2019 eri China National Health Commission.
Nga wayiseewo ennaku musanvu, enkola ya CoV yassibwawo.
Nga 15 Jjanwali 2020 omuntu eyasooka okufa okuva e Wuhan yategeezebwa.
Mu kiseera kye kimu, kawumpuli yayanguwa okuyingira mu bibuga, ssaza, ne mu nsi eziriraanyeewo.
Nga January 20, obulwadde bwa bajjanjabi bwateekebwawo, ekiraga nti obulwadde bwali busobola okuva ku muntu okuyingira mu muntu.
Nga 23, omwezi gwa January ekibuga Wuhan kyasibibwa nga n'entambula z'abantu bonna ziyimiridde.
Nga 24 Ogw'Okutandika okunoonyereza ku bulwadde kuno kwalaga nti, ku balwadde 41 abaakakasibwa, 21 bokka be baakwata butereevu ku katale k'ebyennyanja ak'e Wuhan ekyatwalibwa ng'ekifo ekyatandikawo obulwadde okuva ku nsolo etamanyiddwa.
Nga January 30, WHO yalangirira nti ekirwadde kino kyali kya mu bwangu nnyo mu nsi yonna.
Mu kiseera kino ky'owandiika alipoota eno, ekirwadde kino kyabunye mu China yonna era ne mu nsi endala ezisoba mu 50 okwetooloola ensi yonna (Fig. (Fig.2).
Nga embeera ekyuka mangu, omutindo gw'obulwadde n'obunene bwabwo bikyaliwo okussibwa ku mulamwa.
Ku February 11, 2020, okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku balwadde 8,866 omuli n'abalwadde 4,021 abaakakasibwa nti balina COVID-19 kwalaga ekyeyo eky'akabonero ekisingawo ku kyaakatandika eky'ekirwadde kino nga bwe kiragibwa wammanga (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
