Okugatta ku ekyo, okukuuma obutagwa lubege mu bintu ebivaamu amasannyalaze, okutangira n'okujjanjaba endwadde ez'okubiri n'okufuna ekiddukano, n'okukuuma ebikolwa by'ebitundu eby'omubiri eby'omugaso nabyo bikulu nnyo eri abalwadde ba SARS-CoV-2.
Kimanyiddwa nti ekittabantu kya cytokine kiva ku ngeri obusimu bw'omubiri gye buzibwamu mu balwadde ba SARS ne MERS.
Cytokine storm ye ngeri y'obuvunaanyizibwa bw'okwokya okw'omubiri obubeerawo nga bw'efuluma ebitundu by'ebitundu by'ekizinga ky'ekizinga omuli TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, ne MCP-1.
Zino cytokines zireetera obutoffaali bw'omubiri okufulumya omuwendo omunene ennyo ogw'ebitundu by'omubiri ebiriko eddembe ebireeta ARDS n'okulemererwa kw'ebitundu by'omubiri ebingi.
Okukendeeza ku bikola ku mubiri kikulu nnyo mu kujjanjaba ebiseffuyabufuzi bya cytokine, naddala mu balwadde ab'amaanyi.
Corticosteroids ne tocilizumab, anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, bikozeseddwa okujjanjaba ekirwadde kya cytokine.
Obujjanjabi obulala obw'okumalawo obusimu bw'omubiri obuva mu cytokine storm buzingiramu okufuga obusimu bw'omubiri obuva mu butoffaali bwa T; okuziyiza IFN-γ, IL-1, ne TNF; okuziyiza JAK; blinatumomab; ekirwanyisa ky'obubaka bw'obutundu bwa cytokine 4; n'abaziyiza HDAC.
Steroids, ng'ebikugira obusimu bw'omubiri, zaakozesebwanga nnyo mu kujjanjaba SARS okukendeeza ku bukambwe bw'obulwadde bw'okwokya.
Kyokka, steroids mu ddagala eddene tezaali za muganyulo ku buvune bwa mukenenya mu balwadde ba SARS ne COVID-19.
