Okwongerezaako, olw'ebikolwa eby'obujjanjabi, obumu ku buzibu obuli mu plasma bw'olina okuteekebwako ebirowoozo.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obuwuka obuleeta obulwadde busobola okukyusa obusobozi bw'omubiri obw'okwanukula obulwadde n'okuleetawo cytokine release syndrome, ekiyinza okuteeka obulamu bwo mu kabi.
