Mu ngeri eno, tusobola okwongera okukulaakulanya eddagala ly'okulwanyisa.
TCM ebadde ekozesebwa mu China okumala enkumi n'enkumi z'emyaka okujjanjaba endwadde ez'enjawulo.
Kyokka, ebivaako okusingira ddala byesigamye ku kukwataganya ebintu ebikwatagana mu nkola eyawukana okusinziira ku kujjanjaba obulwadde okusinziira ku ndowooza ya TCM.
Ebitundu ebisinga ebikola ebirimu tebimanyiddwa oba tebitegeerekeka bulungi kubanga kizibu okubikolamu n'okukebera ebitundu ebyo oba entegeka yabyo.
Mu kiseera kino, olw'obutaba na bujjanjabi bulungi era obwenjawulo ku COVID-19, TCM efuuse emu ku nzijanjaba endala ez'omugaso eri abalwadde abalina obubonero obutonotono oba abo abawona okuva mu mbeera ez'amaanyi.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, kapsule ya Shu Feng Jie Du ne Lian Hua Qing Wen zaalagibwa okuba ez'omugaso mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19.
Ebitundu ebirimu okuwona okusinga mu bujjanjabi bw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 byazuulibwa mu bitundu bya China ebiwerako ebyakozesanga TCM mu 87% ku balwadde baabwe, nga mw'otwalidde Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), ne Hunan (50%), ng'ate essaza lya Hubei, erikozesa TCM mu bantu nga 30% bokka ku balwadde ba COVID-19, lye lirina omutindo ogusinga obwavu (13%).
