Nga February 18, 2020, Boli Zhang ne banne bafulumya okunoonyereza okugeraageranya obujjanjabi bw'ebugwanjuba (WM) bwokka n'obujjanjabi obumu obw'eWM n'obwa TCM.
Bazuula nti ebiro ebyetaagisa okuzzaawo ebbugumu ly'omubiri, okuviirako obubonero, n'okusibibwa mu ddwaaliro byali byangu nnyo mu kibiina kya WM+TCM okusinga mu kibiina kya WM yokka.
Ekisinga okweyoleka, omuwendo gw'abalwadde okwonooneka (okuva ku mutono okutuuka ku mukambwe) gwali wansi nnyo mu kibinja kya WM+TCM okusinga ekibinja kya WM yokka (7.4% versus 46.2%) era n'obufudde bwali butono mu kibinja kya WM+TCM okusinga ekibinja kya WM yokka (8.8% versus 39%).
Wadde kiri kityo, obutuufu n'obutebenkevu bwa TCM bukyalinda okunoonyereza okukolebwa ku kigero ekinene era mu bifo bingi.
Kyandibadde kirungi nnyo okumanya engeri enkola gye ekolamu era n'okulaga ebitundu eby'omugaso mu bujjanjabi bwa TCM oba enkola y'okugikwataganya bwe kiba kisoboka.
Abalwadde abalina COVID-19 abateeberezebwa oba abakakasibwa basinga kutya nnyo ekirwadde kino ekirwadde ekikosa ennyo era ekiyinza n'okuviirako okufa, ate abantu abali mu kwekutula nabo bafuna obuzibu, ekiwuubaalo, n'obusungu.
Ate era, obubonero bw'obulwadde nga omusujja, hypoxia, n'okukaaba awamu n'ebizibu ebiva mu bujjanjabi nga obuteebaka obuleetebwa eddagala lya corticosteroids biyinza okuleeta okweraliikirira n'okunyigirizibwa mu birowoozo.
Mu kaseera akasooka ak'okusaasaana kwa SARS, obulwadde bw'obwongo obw'enjawulo nga mw'otwalidde okwennyamira okw'olubeerera, okweraliikirira, okutya, okusanyuka mu birowoozo, obubonero bw'obwongo, okutabuka, n'okwegomba okwetta byalagibwa.
Okuteeka abantu ku ddagala n'okubateeka mu kalantiini, ng'ekitundu ky'obuddukiro bw'ebyobulamu mu bantu olw'okusaasaana kw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19, kiyinza okuleetera abantu okweraliikirira n'okulumwa olw'ebyo ebiva mu bulwadde, okuteekebwa mu kalantiini, n'okuvumirirwa mu maka gaabwe ne mikwano gyabwe.
N'olwekyo, obujjanjabi bw'obulamu obw'ekisenge bulina okuweebwa abalwadde ba COVID-19, abantu abateeberezebwa okuba n'obulwadde buno, n'abantu abakwatagana nabo awamu n'abantu abalala bonna abeetaaga obujjanjabi.
