Kyokka, okufaananako SARS ne MERS, COVID-19 nayo ekwataganyizibwa n'obulwadde obw'amaanyi n'okufa mu balwadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
N'olwekyo, okuzimba enkola y'okulowooza ku bulwadde buno kikulu nnyo eri ebitongole ebikuuma ebyobulamu okussa mu nkola obuweereza bwabyo, naddala mu bitundu ebirimu eby'obugagga ebitono.
