Okukebera mu laabu okw'obulwadde bwa coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) n'akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 ak'ekwataganaako kuzingiramu enkola ez'okumanya akawuka n'ezo ez'okumanya obuwuka obuziyiza obulwadde obuva mu kukwatibwa obulwadde.
Okubeerawo kwa siriimu mu bifaananyi kukakasibwa RT-PCR, ekikebera RNA ya coronavirus.
Akakode kano ka njawulo era kaategekebwa okuzuula RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 yokka.
Kikozesebwa okukakasa endwadde ezisembye oba eziriwo.
Okuzuula obuwuka obwa antibodies (serology) kusobola okukozesebwa mu kujjanjaba n'okulabirira abantu.
Ebigezo by'emirambo biraga abantu bameka abafunye obulwadde, omuli n'abo abalina obubonero obutonotono ennyo okutegeeza oba abataalina bubonero.
Omuwendo gw'abantu abafa obulwadde buno n'omutindo gw'obukuumi bw'ekika mu bantu busobola okutegeerekeka okuva mu biva mu kukebera kuno.
Olw'okugezesa okutono, mu March 2020 tewali nsi yali erina obubaka bwesigika ku bungi bw'abantu abaalina akawuka kano.
Nga 23 Ogwokusatu, tewali ggwanga lyalina bantu basukka 3% be lyakozesa, era waliwo enjawulo ya maanyi mu ngeri okwekebeza gye kukoleddwamu mu mawanga.
Okukyuka kuno era kuyinza okubaako kye kikola ku bungi bw'abantu abafa, era nga mu nsi ezimu abantu bayinza okuba nga basinga nnyo ku muwendo gw'abantu abafa.
Okukozesa real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) okwekebejja kusobola okukolebwa ku bifaananyi by'ebitundu by'omukka ebizuuliddwa mu ngeri ez'enjawulo, omuli ne swab ey'omu nsingo oba ekifaananyi ky'ebisenge.
Ebivaamu bibeerawo mu ssaawa ntono okutuuka ku nnaku 2.
Okukebera kwa RT-PCR okukolebwa n'ebikoola by'omu nsingo kukakasa wiiki esooka ey'obulwadde.
Oluvannyuma akawuka kano kayinza okubula mu kasenge nga bwe kayongera okuzaala mu mawuggwe.
Abantu abakwatiddwa ekirwadde kino bakeberebwa mu wiiki ey'okubiri, ekirala, ekirungo ekiva mu bbanga ekiva mu kkubo ly'omukka ery'omunda nga kikozesebwa kateteri oba nga kikozesebwa nga kikoowa (sputum).
Ekimu ku bigezo bya PCR ebyasooka kyatongozebwa mu Charité mu Berlin mu Jjanwali 2020 nga bikozesa enkola ya reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), era kye kyavaako ebizimbisibwa 250,000 eby'okugabira ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO).
Obwakabaka bwa Bungereza nabwo bwali bufunye ekigezo nga 23 Jjanwali 2020.Kkampuni ya South Korea eya Kogenebiotech yafuna ekigezo ekikugu, ekyesigamiziddwa ku PCR ekirimu ekirungo kya SARS-CoV-2 (PowerChek Coronavirus) nga 28 Jjanwali 2020.
Enoonya gen eya "E" eyagabanyizibwa ne beta coronaviruses zonna, n'ekika kya RdRp ekirimu SARS-CoV-2. Mu China, BGI Group y'emu ku kkampuni ezaasooka okufuna olukusa okuva mu China's National Medical Products Administration olw'okukozesa mu bwangu ekikubiro kya PCR-based SARS-CoV-2. Mu Amerika, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) esasaanya ekikubiro kya 2019-Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) Real-Time RT-PCR Diagnostic Panel eri laabu z'ebyobulamu bw'abantu okuyita mu International Reagent Resource.
Ekimu ku bipimo ebisatu eby'ekika mu nnukuta enkadde ez'ebikemo byaleeta ebivuddeyo ebitazzaamu maanyi olw'ebikozesebwa ebikyamu, n'obutabanguko mu kukebera ku CDC mu Atlanta; kino kyaviirako omuwendo gwa bigezo ebitawera 100 buli lunaku okukolerwako obulungi mu February 2020 yonna.
Ebigezo ebikozesa ebintu bibiri tebyateekebwako bigezo okutuusa nga 28 Febwali 2020, era tekyali okutuusa olwo nti ebitongole bya gavumenti n'ebitundu byabakkiriza okutandika okwekebejja.
Okukeberebwa kwakkirizibwa ekitongole kya Food and Drug Administration wansi w'ekigendererwa eky'okukozesa mu bwangu. Ebitongole bya US eby'obusuubuzi byatandika okwekebejjebwa mu ntandikwa ya March 2020.
Nga 5 omwezi gw'okusatu 2020 LabCorp yalangirira nti okugezesa COVID-19 okusinziira ku RT-PCR kujja kubaawo mu ggwanga lyonna.
Quest Diagnostics mu ngeri y'emu yafuula okugezesa kwa COVID-19 okw'ensi yonna okuba okw'omugaso nga 9 March 2020.
Tewali kukyusa mu bungi; okuterekebwa n'okukolebwako kw'ebifaananyi kulina okukolebwa nga CDC bw'egamba.
Mu Russia, ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kyakuzibwa era ne kifulumizibwa ekitongole kya State Research Center of Virology and Biotechnology VECTOR.
Nga 11 omwezi 2 omwaka 2020, ekigezo kyateekebwako mu nkola y'obujjanjabi. Nga 12 omwezi 3 omwaka 2020, Mayo Clinic yategeezebwa okuba nga yakulaakulanya ekigezo ekikebera obulwadde bwa COVID-19. Nga 13 omwezi 3 omwaka 2020, Roche Diagnostics yafuna olukusa okuva mu kitongole kya FDA olw'ekigezo ekiyinza okukolebwa mu ssaawa 3.5 mu bungi, bwe kityo nga kisobozesa ekyuma kimu okukola ebigezo nga 4,128 mu ssaawa 24.
Nga 19 March 2020, FDA yafulumya olukusa olw'okukozesa mu bwangu (EUA) eri Abbott Laboratories olw'okugezesa ku nkola ya m2000 ya Abbott; FDA yali yafulumya dda olukusa olufaanana olwo eri Hologic, LabCorp, ne Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Nga 21 March 2020, Cepheid naye yafuna EUA okuva ku FDA okwekebejjebwa okutwala eddakiika nga 45.
FDA ekkirizza ekigezo ekikozesa tekinologiya wa isothermal nucleic acid amplification technology mu kifo kya PCR.
Okuva kino bwe tekyetaagisa kuddamu kutonnya mu bbanga lya ssaawa, enkola eno eyinza okuleeta ebivaamu ebirungi mu ddakiika ttaano kyokka ate ebivaamu ebikyamu mu ddakiika kkumi na ssatu.
Mu kiseera kino waliwo ebyuma nga 18,000 mu Amerika era Abbott asuubira okwongera okufulumya ebyuma bino okugezaako ebipimo 50,000 buli lunaku. Ekipimo ekikozesa omubiri ogumu ogukwata ku butundutundu bwa nucleocapsid protein (N protein) obw'akawuka ka corona bwakolebwa mu Taiwan, nga basuubira nti kijja kusobola okuwa ebivudde mu ddakiika 15 okutuuka ku 20 nga bwe kiba ng'okugezesa omulundi gumu.
Okweekenneenya ebitabo mu Maaki 2020 kwalaga nti "ebifaananyi by'omu kifuba tebirina mugaso mu kujjanjaba mu mitendera egy'entandikwa, ng'ate ebizuulibwa mu CT [computer tomography] biyinza okubeerawo wadde ng'obubonero tebunnaba kulabika".
Ebintu ebimanyiddwa ku CT mulimu obutategeerekeka mu multilobar ne ground glass nga bw'ebitundu by'omubiri ebikalu, ebyenjawulo n'ebyennyirira.
Obusungu bw'ekibumba, obuwuka obw'ekyewuunyo n'okunyweza bijjawo ng'obulwadde bwe bweyongera.
Okunoonyereza okugerageranya PCR ne CT mu Wuhan ku kifo ekyatandikawo obulwadde buno kyalaga nti CT erina obusobozi obunene okusinga PCR, wadde nga si ya njawulo nnyo, ng'ebifaananyi byayo bingi bifaanagana n'obubalwadde obulala obwa ppumoni n'obulwadde.
Mu March 2020, American College of Radiology yakubiriza nti "CT teyalina kukozesebwa mu kukebera oba ng'ekikebera eky'olubereberye okuzuula COVID-19". Mu March 2020, CDC yakubiriza PCR mu kukebera okusooka.
Ekimu ku bikwata ku kuddamu kw'omubiri eri ekirwadde kwe kukola obuwuka obuziyiza omuli IgM ne IgG.
Bino biyinza okukozesebwa okuzuula obulwadde mu bantu nga buwezeeko ennaku 7 oluvannyuma lw'okulaga obubonero, okumanya obukuumi, n'okukuuma abantu. Ebipimo biyinza okukolebwa mu laabu z'ekika (CLT) oba okuyita mu kunoonyereza mu kifo w'ojjanjabirwa (PoCT).
Enkola z'okukozesa amasannyalaze mu laboratories ez'ekikugu zijja kusobola okukola ebigezo bino naye okubeerawo kwabyo kujja kwesigama ku sipiidi y'obutonde bwa buli nkola.
Mu CLT ekirobozo ekimu eky'omusaayi ogw'omunda kye gikozesebwa, wadde nga ebipimo ebiteekeddwawo biyinza okukozesebwa okugoberera obuwombeefu bw'omubiri.
Okukola PoCT, ekirungo kimu eky'omusaayi kitwalibwa nga bakubye olusu.
Okwawukana ku nkola ya PCR, eky'okuggya eddagala mu mubiri tekyetaagisa nga tebannaba kukebera. Nga March 26, 2020, FDA yalonda ebitongole 29 ebyategeeza ekitongole nga bwe kyetaagisa era nga kati bisobola okugabya ebigezo byabwe eby'ebitundu eby'omubiri.
Nga 7 Apuli 2020, waliwo ekigezo kimu kyokka ekikkirizibwa FDA wansi w'obuyinza obw'okukozesa mu bwangu. Ku nkomerero ya March 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics ne Epitope Diagnostics baafuna ebikkirizo by'omu Bulaaya ku by'okugezesa byabwe, ebisobola okukebera obuwuka obuziyiza obuwuka obuyitibwa IgG ne IgA mu bifaananyi by'omusaayi.
Obusobozi bw'okwekebeza bukebera mu bipande ebikumi mu ssaawa ntono era nga bw'otyo bwangu okusinga okwekebeza PCR okwa bulijjo okwa RNA eya kawuka.
Obususubi busobola okweyoleka nga wayise ennaku 14 oluvannyuma lw'obulwadde okutandika. Ku ntandikwa ya April, UK yazuula nti tewali na kimu ku byuma ebigezesa obususubi bye yagula ekyali kirungi kukozesebwa.
Hong Kong etaddewo enteekateeka ng'abalwadde abateeberezebwa okubeera awaka, "ekitongole ky'eddembe kijja kuwa omulwadde ekirimu", bafulumya amasuwa, ne bakyaddayo ne bafuna ebiva mu kukebera oluvannyuma lw'ekiseera. Ekibiina kya Bungereza ekya NHS kyalangiridde nti kitambuza enteekateeka y'okwekebejjebwa abalwadde abateeberezebwa okubeera awaka, ekiggyawo akabi k'omulwadde okukosa abalala singa bajja mu ddwaliro oba okuteebereza emmotoka ya bbeereere bw'eba ekozesebwa. Mu kukebera COVID-19 mu mmotoka nga batambuza, omusawo w'ekisawo atwala ekirimu ng'akozesa enkola entuufu.
Amatabi ag'okukozesa ag'okuvuga agambye South Korea okukola ebimu ku bigezo ebikyasinze okuba eby'amangu, ebisingako obunene mu nsi yonna. Mu Bugirimaani, National Association of Statutory Health Insurance Physicians yagamba nga March 2, nti yalina obusobozi bw'ebigezo ebisoba mu 12,000 buli lunaku mu kifo ekirimu abasawo era 10,700 be baakeberebwa mu wiiki eyagiddako.
Ssente z'okwekebejja zisasulwa aba yinsuwa y'obulwadde bw'omusawo bw'alagira ekigezo.
Okusinziira ku ssentebe w'ekitongole kya Robert Koch, Bugirimaani erina obusobozi bw'okugezesa 160,000 buli wiiki.
Okuva nga 19 Ogwokusatu, okugezaako okutambulira mu mmotoka kwaweebwayo mu bibuga ebinene ebiwerako.
Nga 26 Maaki 2020 omuwendo gw'ebigezo byonna ebikoleddwa mu Bugirimaani tegumanyiddwa, kubanga ebivuddemu ebirungi byokka bye byalagiddwa.
Okunoonyereza okwasooka mu laabu kwalaga nti okusinziira ku wiiki y'omulundi 12/2020, obubonero 483,295 bwe bwagezeddwa nga kw'otaddewo n'obw'omulundi 12/2020 era nga 33,491 (6.9%) baazudde nti balina obubonero bwa SARS-CoV-2.Mu Isirayiri, abanoonyereza mu Technion ne Rambam Hospital baakola era ne bagezaako enkola ey'okwekebejja obubonero okuva mu balwadde 64 omulundi gumu, nga bakuŋŋaanya obubonero era nga bongera okugezesa bwokka singa obubonero obukoleddwa bulabika nga bulina obubonero. Mu Wuhan, laabu ey'amangu ya mita 2000 ey'amangu eyatuumiddwa "Huo-Yan" (Olukyayina: 火眼, oba "Fire Eye" mu Lungereza) yaggulwawo BGI nga 5 Febwali 2020, esobola okukebera obubonero obusukka mu 10,000 olunaku.
