Okubalukawo kw'omusujja gw'embizzi mu 2009 ne COVID-19 mu 2020 byaleetera amawanga mangi okwongera okumanya obukulu bw'okunaaba mu ngalo n'ensawo okwekuuma endwadde zino ez'akabi.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, ebipande ebiraga "engeri entuufu ey'okunaaba engalo" byawanikibwa okumpi n'ebinaabiro ebinaabirako engalo mu bifo ebya lukale ne mu bifo by'okunaabiramu mu bifo by'ebitongole ne mu bifo ebiriko bbeeyi mu Bugirimaani.
Ebigambo "okunaaba mu ngalo" kitegeeza okutegeeza omuntu nti tayagala kutwala buvunaanyizibwa ku kintu ekyo oba okwenyigira mu ekyo.
Kiva mu Bayibuli mu Matayo, Pontiyo Piraato we yasuza engalo ze olw'okusalawo okukomerera Yesu Kristo, naye kyafuuka ebigambo ebikozesebwa mu bitundu ebimu eby'Olungereza.
Mu Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atandika okunaaba engalo ze mu kugezaako okunaaba ekibala ky'omutima gwe, nga yeeyimirizaamu olw'ebikolobero bye yakola era n'okwekwasa bba.
Era kizuuliddwa nti abantu, oluvannyuma lw'okujjukira oba okulowooza ku bikolwa ebikyamu, bagezaako okunaaba engalo emirundi mingi okusinga abalala, era bassa ekitiibwa mu byuma ebikozesa okunaaba engalo.
Okugatta ku ekyo, abo abakkirizibwa okunaaba engalo oluvannyuma lw'okulowooza ku bintu ng'ebyo, tebasobola kwenyigira mu bikolwa ebirala "eby'okweggyamu" ebiyinza okubaviirako okufiirwa, gamba ng'okukola nga bannakyewa.
Amadiini galagira abantu okunaaba engalo olw'ensonga ez'obuyonjo n'ez'akabonero. Okunaaba engalo mu ngeri ey'akabonero, nga bakozesa amazzi wabula nga tebanako sabuni okunaaba engalo, kitundu kya bulombolombo bw'okunaaba engalo obuli mu madiini mangi, omuli eddiini ya Bahá'í, ey'Abahindu, Tevilah ne netilat yadayim mu ddiini y'Ekiyudaaya, Lavabo mu Bukristaayo, ne Wudhu mu Busiraamu. Eddiini nazo ziraga abantu okunaaba engalo mu ngeri ey'obuyonjo, naddala oluvannyuma lw'okukola ebintu ebimu.
Enzikiriza y'Abahindu, Abayudaaya n'Abasiraamu esabiriza okunaaba mu ngalo oluvannyuma lw'okukozesa kaabuyonjo.
Era, obu Hindu, obu Budda, Sikh, obu Yuda n'obusiraamu, busaba abantu okunaaba engalo nga tebannalya na buli lwe bamala okulya.
Okufuga akabi akali mu bifo by'emirimu ku COVID-19
Okufuga akabi ku mirimu olw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 kwe kukozesa enkola z'obukuumi n'obulamu mu mirimu okuziyiza akabi ku bulwadde bwa coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Okukwata okw'obulabe mu bifo by'emirimu kwesigama ku kifo ky'omulimu n'omulimu, okusinziira ku kubalirira obulabe obuva mu kusannyaladde, obuzibu bw'obulwadde mu kitundu, n'ebiri mu bulabe bw'abakozi kinnoomu abayinza okuba nga balina COVID-19.
Okusinziira ku kitongole kya U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), emirimu egitali ya bulabe nnyo gy'egenda okukola nga waliwo emikwano mitono n'abantu abalala n'abakozi abalala, nga beetaaga okukola ebintu ebisooka eby'okutangira endwadde, omuli okunaaba engalo, okukubiriza abakozi okusigala awaka singa balwala, empisa z'okussa ekirwadde, n'okukuuma obuyonjo n'okuggya obuwuka obutali bukoowu mu kifo gye bakolera.
Emirimu egirina akabi akatono giteekamu emirimu egiba gyetaaga okusisinkana abantu emirundi mingi oba okumpi ennyo abatamanyiddwa oba abateeberezebwa okuba nga balina COVID-19, naye bayinza okusasanyizibwa olw'okusaasaanyizibwa mu bantu oba olw'okutambula mu nsi yonna.
Kino kizingiramu abakozi abalina enkolagana n'abantu abalala nga mu masomero, mu bifo ebirimu abantu abangi, n'ebifo ebimu ebirimu abantu abangi abatunda ebintu.
Okuziyiza akabi mu kibinja kino, ng'oggyeeko ebintu ebisookerwako okukuuma obulwadde, kuzingiramu okufuuyira empewo nga bakozesa ebiwaawaawaatiro by'empewo eby'amaanyi, okutangira okukususa, n'okuba n'ebikozesebwa eby'okukuuma omuntu singa afuna COVID-19.
OSHA eraga nti abakozi b'ebyobulamu n'ab'omu ggwanika ly'abafu ababeera n'omuntu amanyiddwa oba agambibwa okuba ne COVID-19 baba mu kabi k'okufuna akawuka, ekyeyongera okuba akabi ak'amaanyi ennyo singa abakozi bakola emirimu egisobozesa omuntu okufuna akawuka oba okukuŋŋaanya oba okukwata ebifaananyi by'omuntu amanyiddwa oba agambibwa okuba ne COVID-19.
Okukuuma obubenje obuba bukyetaagisa abakozi bano kuzingiramu okufuga eby'obuzaaliranwa nga mu bisenge ebibaamu empewo ez'omukka omubi, n'ebyuma ebikuuma omuntu mu ngeri esaanira omulimu.
Okusaasaana kwa COVID-19 kuyinza okuba n'ebivaako ebitali bimu mu bifo eby'emirimu.
Abakozi bayinza obutabeera ku mulimu olw'okulwala, okwetaaga okulabirira abalala, oba okutya okutebenkeza.
Enkola y'eby'obusuubuzi eyinza okukyuka, mu ngeri y'ebintu ebisabibwa, n'engeri y'okufunamu ebintu bino (ng'okugula mu biseera ebitali bya sipiidi oba okuyita mu kuweereza oba okutwala ebintu mu maka g'omuntu).
Eky'enkomerero, ebyamaguzi ebiva mu bitundu ebikoseddwa ennyo ekirwadde kya COVID-19 biyinza okuyimirizibwa. Enteekateeka y'okwetegekera n'okwanukula endwadde ez'okusaasaanya eyinza okukozesebwa okulambika ebikolwa eby'okukuuma.
Enteekateeka zino zikwata ku miwendo gy'obulabe egikwatagana n'ebifo eby'enjawulo eby'emirimu n'emirimu egitali gimu, omuli ensibuko z'obulabe, ebintu ebireeta obubenje okuva mu maka n'ebitundu by'abantu, n'ebintu ebireeta obubenje eri abakozi kinnoomu gamba ng'obukadde oba obulwadde obw'olukonvuba.
Era batulaga enkola ez'okukuuma ezetaagisa okugonjoola obuzibu obwo, n'enteekateeka ez'okwerinda mu mbeera eziyinza okujjawo olw'okusaasaana kw'obulwadde.
Enteekateeka z'okwetegekera endwadde ez'obukaba n'okuziyiza ziyinza okusinziira ku magezi agaweebwa ku buli lukya ku mulembe oba ku mutendera gwa wansi.
Ebigendererwa by'okwanukula ku bulwadde buno bizingiramu okukendeeza ku kusasaanyizibwa mu bakozi, okukuuma abantu abalina akabi k'okufuna obuzibu mu bulamu, okukuuma emirimu gy'obusuubuzi, n'okukendeeza ku bikolwa ebikyamu ku bitongole ebirala mu bulambe bwabwe.
Obuzibu bw'obulwadde mu kitundu ekifo ekikolerwamu bizineesi bukwata ku by'okuddamu ebiweebwa.
Enkola y'okukuuma obuwuka mu kifo ekirimu akabi, y'emu ku ngeri ezikozesebwa mu kukuuma obulamu bw'abantu n'obukuumi bw'emirimu, okuteeka mu kibinja obuwuka obukuuma obuwuka.
W'osobola okuggyawo obulabe bwa COVID-19, obugenderevu obusingayo obulungi bwe bufuzi bwa yinginiya, obufuzi bw'eby'obufuzi, n'obw'enkomerero ebyuma ebikuuma omuntu.
Okufuga obuzungu kuzingiramu okwawula abakozi okuva ku bulabe obuva ku mirimu nga tebasinziira ku nneeyisa ya bakozi, era eyinza okuba enkola esinga okuba ey'omugaso mu by'ensimbi.
Obufuzi bw'emirimu nkyukakyuka mu nkola y'emirimu oba enkola eziteetaagisa omukozi oba oyo akukozesa okubaako ky'akola.
Ebyuma ebikuuma omuntu (PPE) bitwalibwa okuba nga tebikyakola nnyo ng'ebigezo by'obuyambi n'eby'obufuzi, naye bisobola okuyamba okuziyiza obukuumi obumu.
Ebintu byonna ebikozesebwa omuntu ku bubwe birina okulondebwa okusinziira ku kabi akali ku mukozi, okusabibwa nga bwe kisaanira (ng'eby'okusaabiramu), okwambala obutayosa n'okwambala obulungi, okwekebejjebwa obutayosa, okukuumibwa, n'okukyusibwa nga bwe kyetaagisa, n'okuggibwa, okulongoosebwa, n'okuteekebwa oba okusaanyizibwawo mu ngeri esaanira okwewala obuwuka.
Okusinziira ku U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), emirimu egirina akabi akatono ennyo mu kwekebeza, girina enkolagana ntono n'abantu abalala n'abo be bakolera.
Emitendera gy'okutangira endwadde egiragiddwa mu bifo byonna ebikozesebwa mulimu okunaaba engalo obutayosa, okukubiriza abakozi okusigala awaka bwe baba balwadde, empisa ez'okusaabala omuli okusaabala n'okusiiba, okuteekawo obugoye n'ebikozesebwa mu kusaabala ebintu, okwetegekera okukola emirimu ng'oyita ku ssimu oba okusenguka mu biseera eby'enjawulo bwe kiba kyetaagisa, okugaana abakozi okukozesa ebyuma n'ebikozesebwa abalala, n'okukuuma obuyonjo n'okusaanyaawo obuwuka mu bifo ebikozesebwa.
Okumanya amangu n'okwekutula ku bantu abayinza okuba nga balwadde, ddaala ya maanyi nnyo mu kukuuma abakozi, bakasitoma, abagenyi, n'abalala ku mulimu.
Ekitongole kya Amerika ekivunaanyizibwa ku kukuuma endwadde (CDC) kikubiriza abakozi abalina obubonero bw'obulwadde obw'omukka obwa maanyi okubeera awaka okutuusa nga bawonye ekirwadde ky'omukka, obubonero bw'ekirwadde, n'obubonero obulala bwonna okumala essaawa 24 nga tebasseeko ddagala erigema ekirwadde oba eddagala eddala erikyusa obubonero, n'obutemu bwa ddwaliro bw'obulwadde okuba obwenkukutufu, okukkiriza abakozi okusigala awaka okulabirira omu ku b'omu maka abalwadde, n'okuba abakozi bamanyi bulungi amateeka gano.
Okusinziira ku OSHA, emirimu egiriko akabi akatono mwe muli egigya mu kusisinkananga n'abantu abatamanyiddwa oba abateeberezebwa okuba n'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 naye nga bayinza okuba nga balina obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 olw'obutambuze mu kitundu ekifo ky'emirimu, oba olw'okuba omuntu oyo abadde atambudde mu nsi endala gye buvuddeko n'agenda mu kifo ekirimu obulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Bano bazingiramu abakozi abalina enkolagana n'abantu bonna gamba nga mu masomero, mu bifo ebirimu abantu abangi, ne mu bifo ebimu eby'amaduuka.Engineering controls for this and higher risk groups include installing high-efficiency air filters, increasing ventilation rates, installing physical barriers such as clear plastic sneeze guards, and installing a drive-through window for customer service.Engineering controls for this and higher risk groups include encouraging sick workers to stay at home, replacing face-to-face meetings with virtual communications, establishing staggered shifts, discontinuing nonessential to locations with ongoing COVID-19 outbreaks, developing emergency communications plans including a forum for answering workers' concerns, providing workers with up-to-date education and training on COVID-19 and risk factors, protective resources who may need to promote protecting and how to use it, posting personal protective equipment and providing a regular personal hygiene environment, washing goggles, and other protective measures to workers's work, including washing a mask, hand-washing, and hand-washing on the face and hands, and other protective measures.
Abakozi abali mu kibinja kino kya kabi tebatera kwetaaga kukozesa masiki.
Omuntu bw'alwala mu nnyonyi, okufuga okutuufu okukuuma abakozi n'abagenyi abalala kuzingiramu okwawula omuntu omulwadde n'abalala ku ddaala lya ffuuti 6, okulonda omu ku bakozi b'ennyonyi okumuweereza, n'okuwa omuntu omulwadde akaapu k'amaaso oba okumusaba okubikka akamwa n'olubeerera ng'akomba oba ng'asuubula.
Abakozi mu kabine basaanidde okwambala amaggaloosi ag'eddagala ag'okukozesa ng'olwo nga balabirira omugenyi omulwadde oba nga bakwata ku bintu ebiva mu mubiri oba ebiyinza okuba nga byonoonese, era oboolyawo n'eby'okukozesa okw'okwekweka okw'enjawulo singa omugenyi mulwadde alina omusujja, okukosebwa okw'olumu, oba okuzibuwalirwa okussa.
Ebikonde n'ebintu ebirala eby'okukozesa olina okubitwala mu nsawo eziriko obuwuka era ebitundu ebyonooneddwa birina okuyonjoolwa n'okusaanyizibwawo oluvannyuma. Ku by'entambula z'eby'obwannannyini, omuli n'entalo z'obubudamu n'entalo endala ez'abatambuze, okuziyiza obuzibu kuzingiramu okuyimiriza olugendo ng'oli mulwadde, n'okweyawula ku bantu abalala n'okutegeeza abasawo b'entambula mu bwangu ddala singa omuntu afuna ekikulukuto oba obubonero obulala ng'ali ku mmeeri.
Ekirungi, okulondoola eby'ekisawo kulina kubeera mu kabina k'omuntu eyekusifu. Ku masomero n'ebitongole ebirabirira abaana, CDC ekubiriza okuggalwawo okumala akaseera akatono okuyonja oba okusaanya obuwuka singa omuntu alina obulwadde abeera mu kizimbe ky'essomero, ka kibe nti abadde mu kitundu.
Bwe wabaawo ekirwadde ekikosa abantu, enkola z'okwawula abantu ku balala zisobola okukozesebwa gamba ng'okuggya ebikwekweto, enkuŋŋaana n'okukuŋŋaana okw'abantu abangi gamba nga okutendekebwa oba okusomesa abantu oba okulya mu kisaawe, okwongera obudde wakati w'ebikopo, okwongeza obudde bw'abantu okuyingira n'okuggya, okukendeeza abagenyi abatali ba muwendo, n'okukozesa ekifo eky'enjawulo mu ofiisi y'ebyobulamu eri abaana abalina obubonero obufaanana ng'obwa ssenyiga.
Bwe wabaawo okusasaanyizibwa okw'amaanyi mu kitundu, ng'oggyeko enkola z'okusigala ku bbali, okugoba abayizi mu masomero kuyinza okwongerwako. Eri abakozi b'eby'okwerinda abakola emirimu egy'olunaku lwonna, CDC etwala nti akabi ak'akabi ku bulamu katono.
Abakwasisa amateeka abateekwa okukolagana n'abantu abakakasibwa oba abateeberezebwa okuba ne COVID-19 bakubirizibwa okugoberera ebiragiro bye bimu ng'abakola ku by'obujjanjabi obw'amangu, omuli eby'okukozesa eby'okwerinda.
Singa wabaawo okukwatagana wakati w'abantu nga bakwatibwa, abakozi balina okunaaza n'okufuuyira obugoye bwabwe n'ebikozesebwa nga tebannaba kubikozesa bukozesa ekirongoosa awaka oba ebikukuta, era bagoberere enkola y'emirimu eya bulijjo mu kukweka n'okusa ebikozesebwa bya PPE n'okukuuma n'okwoza engoye.
OSHA etwala abakozi abamu mu byobulamu n'abakola ku by'okuziika nga bebali mu mbeera ez'omutawaana oba ez'omutawaana ennyo.
Emirimu egirimu akabi akali mu kukwatibwa egiri mu kujjanjaba, okuwagira, mu laabu, n'abakozi b'ebidduka eby'ekisawo abategeezebwa oba abateeberezebwa okuba nga balina COVID-19.
Bino bifuuka ebizibu eby'amaanyi ennyo singa abakozi bakola enkola ezireeta akawuka oba okukuŋŋaanya oba okukwata ebipimo okuva ku balwadde ba COVID-19 abamanyiddwa oba abateeberezebwa.
Enkola eziva mu buwunga obuba mu mmunye z'ezo mwe muli intubation, enkola y'okuteekawo ekikulukusa, bronchoscopy, enkola z'amannyo n'ebigezo, oba okunoonya ebifaananyi.
Emirimu egy'ekizikiza eky'amaanyi mu kifo awaabirwa emirambo g'abantu mulimu abakozi abeenyigira mu kuteekateeka emirambo gy'abantu abamanyiddwa oba abateeberezebwa okuba n'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu kiseera eky'okufa kwabwe; bano baba n'akabi ak'amaanyi ennyo singa bakola okuziika. Ebiragiro ebirala eby'obukodyo ku bantu bano ab'akabi ennyo bizingiramu ebisenge eby'okwekutula ku balwadde abamanyiddwa oba abateeberezebwa okuba n'obulwadde bwa COVID-19, nga mw'otwalidde n'embeera y'okuteebereza enziika y'enfuufu.
Okufuuyira omukka gw'obutiti oguyitirivu kiyinza okuba nga kyetaagisa mu bifo ebimu eby'obujjanjabi n'eby'okuziika.
Ebitundu by'ebikozesebwa birina okukwatibwa n'obwegendereza obw'omugaso oguli ku mutendera ogwa 3.
Ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) kikubiriza abalwadde abajja mu ggwanga okuteekebwa mu bifo eby'enjawulo eby'okulinda okusinziira ku kuba nti balina obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obwekwekwekeddwa. Ng'oggyeeko PPE endala, OSHA ekubiriza ebyuma ebikozesebwa okufuuyira empewo eri abo abakolera mu ffuuti 6 ez'abalwadde abamanyiddwa okuba, oba abateeberezebwa okuba, abalina obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2, n'abo abakola enkola ezireeta omukka oguyitibwa aerosol.
Mu Amerika, ebiwaawaatiro ebikozesebwa mu maaso ebiwaanibwa ekitongole kya National Institute of Occupational Health and Health Services (NIOSH) oba ebirongoofu birina kukozesebwa mu nteekateeka y'okukuuma okw'omu byuma ebikwatagana, ebiteekebwa mu buwandiike, omuli okugezesa omubiri, okutendekebwa, n'okwekebezebwa mu malwaliro.
Ebika ebirala eby'ebikozesebwa mu kuwummula biyinza okuwa obukuumi obusingawo n'okwongera ku buweerero bw'abakozi. Ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'obulamu tekisaba bantu kwambala bikonde, kubanga COVID-19 bulwadde obuva mu ngeri y'okussaamu omukka mu kifo ky'okusaasaanyizibwa mu butto bw'omubiri.
WHO esabiriza abantu abakola ku bifo ebijjanjabirwamu okwambala masiki z'ekinnansi zokka.
Eri abo abakung'aanya ebipimo eby'okussa okuva mu, okulabirira, oba okutambuza abalwadde ba COVID-19 nga tewali nkola ya kussa ekirimu omukka, WHO esabiriza okukozesa akabonero k'omu by'omubiri, obugole, oba ekyuma ekikuuma amaaso, ekkanzu, n'engalo.
Bwe wabaawo enkola ey'okuteeka akawuka mu mubiri, akaweke ka ku maaso k'omusawo kakyusibwa n'ekikozesebwa ku kussaamu obusawo obwa N95 oba FFP2.
Olw'okuba obuyambi bw'ensi yonna obw'ebikozesebwa eby'okwerinda mu mubiri tebuba bumala, WHO ekubiriza okukendeeza ku bwetaavu bw'ebikozesebwa eby'okwerinda mu ngeri ey'ekika kya telemedicine, okuggya ebisiba gamba nga amadirisa, okuleka abo bokka abeenyigira mu kulabirira omuntu mu ngeri ey'obwomu okuyingira mu kisenge omuli omulwadde wa COVID-19, okukozesa ebikozesebwa eby'okwerinda eby'obwomu ebyetaagisa mu ngeri ey'enjawulo, okweyongera okukozesa ekifuba kye kimu nga tekiggibwa nga bwe balabirira abalwadde ab'enjawulo abalina obulwadde bwe bumu, okulondoola n'okutuukiriza enteekateeka y'ebikozesebwa eby'okwerinda mu mubiri, n'okugaana okukozesa eby'okwekubisa ku bantu abatalina bubonero.
