b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) enzyme ekwataganyizibwa ku kisenge eky'ebweru (cell membranes) eky'obutoffaali mu mawuggwe, emitima, omutima, ensigo, n'ebinywa.
ACE2 ekendeeza ku bikolwa bya enzyme eya angiotensin-converting (ACE) ng'ekendeeza omuwendo gwa angiotensin-II era ng'eyongera Ang ((1-7) nga kino ekikola eddagala erisobola okujjanjaba endwadde z'omutima.ACE2 era ekola ng'omutendera oguyingira mu butoffaali bwa koonavayiira ezimu.
Ensibuko y'enzyme eri abantu etera okuyitibwa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 kye kyuma ekirimu zinc ekisangibwa ku maaso g'ebisenge bya endothelial n'ebirala.
Protein ya ACE2 erimu endagamuntu ya peptidase M2 ey'ekigero kya N n'endagamuntu ya collectrin ey'ekigero kya C ey'ekigero ky'amino acid.
ACE2 ye protein ey'ekika ekika ekimu ey'ekika ekisooka, nga erina enzyme ezikola ku ttaka erisibiddwa ku maaso g'ensiri mu mawuggwe n'ebitundu ebirala.
Ekitundu kya ACE2 ekibeera ebweru w'ensiri kiva mu kitundu eky'omu kisenge nga kiva mu enziimu endala eyitibwa sheddase, era ekirongoose ekirungo ekivaamu kifuluma mu musaayi era oluvannyuma ne kifuluma mu siriimu.
ACE2 eri mu bitundu bingi: ACE2 esangibwa ku mulamwa gw'ebitundu ebingi eby'ekibumba ekika II, enterocytes ez'omu lubuto, endothelial cells ez'omusaayi n'ez'omusaayi n'ebitundu by'omubiri ebirongoofu mu bitundu bingi.
Okulaga ACE2 mRNA era kusangibwa mu cerebral cortex, striatum, hypothalamus, ne brainstem.
Omulimu omukulu ogwa ACE2 kwe kukola ng'omugere ku ACE.
ACE ekwata angiotensin I hormone mu angiotensin II ekwata ku nnyingo z'omubiri.
ACE2 esobya carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine okuva mu angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) era n'egifuula angiotensin (1- 7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 era esobola okusalaamu peptidi endala omuli [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, ne ghrelin.
ACE2 era eteekawo entambula y'omuzibe gw'amino acid SLC6A19 era nga y'eyamba mu bulwadde bwa Hartnup.
Ng'ekirungo ekidduka mu mubiri, ACE2 y'ey'asinga okuyingira mu butoffaali bwa koonavirusi ezimu, omuli HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (akawuka akaleeta SARS); ne SARS-CoV-2 (akawuka akeeta COVID-19).
Okusingawo, okukwata akawuka ka S1 aka SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV2 ku kika kya ACE2 ku maaso g'ensiri kivaamu endocytosis n'okusenguka kwa kawuka ne enziimu mu endosomes eziri munda mu nsiri.
Enkola eno ey'okuyingira era yeetaagisa okuggya protein ya S mu mubiri nga eyitibwa serine protease TMPRSS2, okuziyiza okukoleddwa nga kwekenneenyezebwa mu kiseera kino ng'engeri y'okujjanjaba. Kino kireetedde abamu okulowooza nti okukendeeza ku mutindo gwa ACE2 mu butoffaali, kiyinza okuyamba mu kulwanyisa obulwadde.
Kyokka, ebibiina by'obwannannyini bingi n'ebitongole ebirondoola beeyongedde okubawa obujjanjabi obwekubaddewo obwa ACE inhibitor ne ARB.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu ngeri entegeke obulungi n'okwekebera okwakubibwa nga Jjulaayi 11, 2012, kwazuula nti "okukozesa ACE inhibitors kwava ku kukendeera kw'obulabe obw'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe obwa 34% bw'ogeraageranya n'obw'abantu abalala".
Ate era, "obulabe bw'ekibumba bwakendeera n'abalwadde abajjanjabiddwa ACE inhibitors abaalina akabi ak'ekibumba, naddala abo abalina sitiroki n'okuddirira kw'omutima.
Okukozesa ACE inhibitors nakyo kyakolebwa okukendeeza ku kufa okwali kuvudde ku bulwadde bw'amawuggwe, wadde ng'ebyavudde byabadde bitono okusinga eby'obulabe bw'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe.
Ekika kya ACE2 ekivudde mu bantu (rhACE2) kirina okuba eddagala eppya mu bulwadde bw'amaviivi, era kirabise nga kikyusa obwagazi bw'omusaayi mu mawuggwe n'omukka mu bisolo ebito ebirina obulwadde bw'obutabanguko bw'omukka obuva ku lipopolysaccharide.
Ekiseera rhACE2 ky'ekyalimu eky'okusatu mu bantu kiri ssaawa 10 era ekikolwa kitandika mu ddakiika 30 ng'oggyeeko ekikolwa (ebiseera) eky'essaawa 24.
Ebizuuliddwa bingi biraga nti rhACE2 eyinza okuba eddagala erisuubizo eri abo abalina obutagumiikiriza ku biwuka ebiziyiza enkola ya renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) oba mu ndwadde nga angiotensin II ey'okuyingizibwa egenda mu maaso. rhACE2 eyateekebwa mu nsigo esobeddwa mu kukebera kwa ddwaliro mu kujjanjaba obulwadde obwa ddwaaliro.
b'Ebipya bya COVID-19 byebyo ebikozesebwa ku ssimu ezikozesebwa ku masimu ebyateekebwawo okuyamba mu kunoonyereza ku bantu abaayingidde mu mbeera y'ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe 2019-20, kwe kugamba, enkola y'okumanya abantu ("ab'omukwano") abayinza okuba nga baatuuse ku muntu alina obulwadde.
Ebintu bingi byakuzibwa oba byalagulwa, nga n'obuyambi bwa gavumenti mu bitundu ebimu.
Enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okuzimba app z'okuzuula abantu zikoleddwa.
Okweraliikirira ku nsonga z'obwannannyini, okusingira ddala ku nkola ezesigamiziddwa ku kutegera ekifo ky'abakozesa app.
Ebirala ebitajja kulabika mu bantu mwe muli okukozesa obubonero bwa Bluetooth okuzuula wa w'ali okumpi n'amasimu amalala.
Nga 10 April 2020, Google ne Apple baalangirira nti bagenda kwongera ku nkola y'okuwagira app ez'ekika kya Bluetooth mu nkola za Android ne iOS.
Mu China, gavumenti ya China, ng'ekolagana ne Alipay, yatongozza app esobozesa bannansi okukebera oba nga babadde bakwatagana n'abantu abalina COVID-19.
Kigenda mu nkola mu bibuga bya China ebisoba mu 200. Mu Singapore, enkola eyitibwa TraceTogether ekozesebwa.
App eno yakolerwa ekibiina kya IT eky'omu kitundu, ne kifulumizibwa nga open source era nga ejja okuweebwa gavumenti. North Macedonia yatongozza "StopKorona!", app eya Bluetooth okuzuula abantu abayinza okuba nga balwadde era n'okuwa obuyambi obw'amangu eri abakungu b'ebyobulamu.
App eno yateekebwawo Minisitule y'Obuwulize n'Eby'empuliziganya n'Eby'obulamu.
Nga 14 April 2020, app yali erindirira okuteekebwako omukono okuva mu Google Play Store ne Apple App Store.
Nga 12 April, gavumenti yagamba nti app y'okunoonya abantu be yali ekulaakulana, era yandibadde esobola okukozesebwa mu wiiki ntono. App efaanana bw'etyo etegekeddwa mu Ireland, ne mu Bufalansa ("StopCovid").
Australia ne New Zealand buli kimu bifumiitiriza ku nkola ezesigamiziddwa ku nkola ya TraceTogether eya Singapore ne BlueTrace protocol. Russia etegese okuleeta enkola ya geofencing eri abalwadde ba COVID-19 ababeera e Moscow, eyagala okukakasa nti tebava waka.
Ross Anderson, profesa w'obwannakyewa ku Cambridge University, yataddewo ebizibu ebingi ebyeyolekera mu nkola ezikozesa app, omuli n'ebikyamu n'obutaba na mugaso singa app ekozesebwa abantu batono.
Okweggyawo okutya okw'okusaasaanya enkola za "coronavirus" ez'obulimba oba ez'obulabe, Apple yateeka ekkomo ku ngeri ki ez'ebitongole ebiyinza okuteeka enkola za "coronavirus" mu App Store, nga zikoma ku bitongole "ebyabufuzi" oba ebitongole ebirina erinnya eddungi.
Google ne Amazon bataddewo amateeka ge gamu.
Abalwanirizi b'obwannannyini baalaga nti beeraliikirivu ku ngeri okulondoola abantu bangi gye kuyinza okukwata ku bakozesa programu za coronavirus, naddala ku ngeri enkola y'okulondoola eyakolebwa okugonjoola obulwadde bwa coronavirus gye yandiggibwamu ng'obulabe bumaze okuggwa.
Amnesty International n'ebitongole ebirala ebisukka mu 100 byafulumizza ekirangiriro nga biwakanya okukugira okulondoola okw'engeri eno.
Ebibiina bino byateekeddwako ebintu munaana ku pulojekiti za gavumenti:
okunoonyereza ku bintu kutandikiddewo "mu mateeka, kwetaagisa era kusaanira";
ebiragiddwa ku kulabirira n'okukuuma byetaaga okubeera n'ebiragiro ebiteetaagisa;
okukozesa kw'obubaka kwandibadde kukoma ku bigendererwa bya COVID-19;
Obukuumi bw'obubaka n'obutayitanga bujja kuba bulina okukuumibwa era ne bulaga nti bukuumibwa okusinziira ku bujulizi;
okulondoola kw'ebitonde by'ensi kwandibadde kwewala okwongera okuleetawo enjawukana n'okusuulibwa ku ludda lw'abantu;
Okugabana kw'amawulire n'abantu ab'okusatu kwandibadde kuteekebwa mu mateeka;
wandibaddewo ebikuuma eri ebikolwa eby'okukozesa obubi era n'eddembe ly'obutuuze okuddamu ebikolwa eby'okukozesa obubi;
"Okwetaba okw'amakulu" okuva mu "b'omukutu bonna" kwandibadde kwetaagisa, nga mw'otwalidde n'abanoonyereza ku byobulamu n'ebibiina ebisoomoozebwa. Ekibiina kya German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) ne Reporters Without Borders (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) nabo baafulumya olukalala lw'ebiteeso.
Enteekateeka ya Google ne Apple ey'okugonjoola ekizibu ky'okwetegereza okw'olubeerera nga baggya enkola y'okuzuula ababi mu nkola zaabwe ez'okukozesa ebyuma nga tebikyetaagisa.
Ensi ezimu zaakozesa enkola y'okuteeka ebifo mu mukutu mu kifo ky'okukozesa app, nga kino kyamalawo obwetaavu bw'okukuba app n'obusobozi bw'okwewala okuteeka ebifo.
Mu Israel, okuzuula ku mutimbagano kwakkirizibwa.
Enkola ez'oku mutimbagano ezirina obuyinza ku bifo by'obudde ebitafulumizibwa zirina obuzibu obw'amaanyi ku bubwo obw'obutonde.
Kyokka, si buli nkola ey'omutanda ow'omunda nti yeetaaga okufuna obubaka ku kifo omuntu ky'ali; enkola ez'okukuuma ebyama zikoleddwa ezikozesa omutanda ow'omunda okuwuliziganya (laba akatundu wammanga).
Mu South Korea, enkola etayitira mu app yakozesebwa okukola okuzuula abantu be baatuukirako.
Mu kifo ky'okukozesa app eyabulijjo, enkola eno yakuŋŋaanya obubaka okuva mu nsibuko ez'enjawulo omuli obubaka obuva ku byuma bya simu n'obw'empaka z'ebirabo, era n'ebikozesa okuleeta obubaka okuyita mu bubaka obw'omu kiwandiiko eri abantu abayinza okuba nga balwadde.
Ng'oggyeeko okukozesa obubaka buno okulabula abantu be bayinza okuwuliziganya nabo, gavumenti era efulumizza obubaka obukwata ku kifo kino, ekintu ekikkirizibwa olw'enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi ezakolebwa mu mateeka agafuga eby'obuntu oluvannyuma lw'okusaasaana kw'obulwadde bwa MERS mu ggwanga eryo.
Obubaka buno bubeerawo eri abantu bonna okuyita mu programu n'emikutu emingi. Ensi nga Germany, zisuubira okukozesa enkola ez'okukuuma ebyamaama n'okukuuma ebyama.
Nga 6 April 2020, by'omanyiso byali tebinnafulumizibwa.
Okukebera okwekuuma ebyama by'omuntu ye ndowooza etambulidde ddala, nga waliwo ebitabo bingi eby'okunoonyereza ebimaze emyaka nga 2013. Nga 7 Apuli 2020, ebibinja by'abakugu ebisoba mu kkumi na bibiri byali bikolera ku by'okuddamu eby'omukwano ebikuuma ebyama by'omuntu, gamba ng'okukozesa Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) okuwandiika obunene bw'omukozesa eri amasimu amalala.
Wabula, PEPP-PT ye nkola ey'okukwataganya erimu enkola ez'enjawulo ez'enjawulo, era si nkola emu yokka. Enkola ez'enjawulo ez'enjawulo z'ezo ez'enjawulo ezirimu Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact Numbers (TCN, fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN), Privacy Sensitive Protocols and Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT) n'endala.
Mu nkola eno, obubaka obwekusifu tebuva ku kyuma, era okufananya kwonna kukolebwa ku kyuma.
Ekibinja kya Privacy Group ku MIT Media Lab kibadde kikulaakulanya SafePaths, enkola y'okukozesa enkola ez'okukuuma ebyama nga bakuŋŋaanya era nga bakozesa ebifo oba amakubo agayita mu kwesooka kw'obutonde okusinziira ku kusaasaana kwa COVID-19.
Byesigamiziddwa ku kunoonyereza okuva mu whitepaper "Apps Gone Rogue: Okukuuma Obuwombeefu mu Mulwadde" eyafulumiziddwa mu Maaki 2020. Okufuba okulala okufaananako kwe kwa SafeTrace platform eya Enigma MPC, kkampuni ekulaakulanya tekinologiya ez'obwombeefu ezaatandikibwawo ku MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ekozesa tekinologiya wa hardware omukuumi okuleka abakozesa okugabana ebifo n'ebyobulamu n'abakozesa abalala n'abakungu, nga teboonoona byabulamu bya data.
Nga 5 Apuli 2020, ekibiina kya TCN Coalition eky'ensi yonna kyatandikibwawo ebibinja ebibumbiddwa awamu nga bikolera ku nkola y'emu era nga n'ebiragiro bikontana, nga ekigendererwa kyabyo kwe kukendeeza ku kusattulukuka, n'okusobozesa okukolagana okw'ensi yonna mu kutereka n'okulangirira app, ekintu ekikulu ekireetera abantu okugafuna.
Nga 9 Apuli 2020, gavumenti ya Singapore yalangirira nti yali efudde enkola ya BlueTrace ekozesebwa app ya gavumenti.
Nga 10 April 2020, Google ne Apple, amakampuni agafuga Android ne iOS, yalangirira enteekateeka y'okulondoola abantu, nga bagamba nti kijja kukuuma ebyama, okusinziira ku buwandiike bwa Bluetooth Low Energy technology n'obwekusifu.
Baafulumizza n'ennyingo z'ebikozesebwa mu nkola eno.
Okusinziira ku Apple ne Google, enkola egendereddwamu okusaasaanyizibwa mu mitendera esatu:
Okusaasaanya eby'okukozesa okusobozesa gavumenti okukola programu z'okuzuula obulwadde bwa koona ezikuuma ebyama byazo
okugatta enkola eno butereevu mu iOS ne Android, Google ne Apple bateekateeka okugonjoola ebizibu eby'okukozesa n'okukuuma ebiragiro nga basooka okugabira enkola eno nga bayita mu kukyusa enkola y'emirimu, era oluvannyuma ne bagiggyamu mu ngeri y'emu ng'obulabe buwedde.
b'Okukyusa eddagala (also amanyiddwa nga drug repurposing, re-profiling, re-tasking oba therapeutic switching) kwe kuddamu kukozesa eddagala erikkiriziddwa okujjanjaba obulwadde oba embeera y'obulamu eya njawulo okusinga eyo gyeyaliko.
Kino kye kimu ku bintu ebiyigirizibwa mu kunoonyereza okw'obusawo okuteekebwawo eddagala ery'obukuumi era ery'omugaso eri COVID-19.
Ebitundu ebirala eby'okunoonyereza bizingiramu okussaawo eddagala ly'omusaayi ery'okulwanyisa COVID-19 n'okuyingiza plasma mu muntu ng'awona. SARS-CoV-2 erina protein ezisobola okukozesebwa eddagala nga 66, nga buli emu erina ebitundu eby'enjawulo ebikwatagana.
Okweekenneenya ebifo ebyo eby'okwekwata ku COVID-19 kiwa enteekateeka entuufu ey'okwekulaakulanya eddagala erigema obuwuka erigema obutwa.
Ku bizinensi ezisinga obukulu SARS-CoV-2 z'ezikubiddwaamu ze papain-like protease, RNA-dependent RNA polymerase, helicase, S protein, ne ADP ribophosphatase.
Hussein A, et al beekenneenyezza ebintu ebiwerako ebiyinza okukozesebwa oluvannyuma ne babikozesa bulungi ne babinoonyerezaako okusobola okulaba engeri gye bifaanaganamu n'eddagala erisinga okuba ery'ekika kye limu erikkirizibwa okusobola okwanguya okuteekebwawo eddagala ery'amaanyi erirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 mu kunoonyereza kwe okwasooka okubuulirirwa mu kunoonyereza okw'ekika kya ddwaliro.
Chloroquine ddagala erirwanyisa omusujja gw'ensiri era ekozesebwa okulwanyisa endwadde ezimu ez'obutawaanya.
Nga 18 March, WHO yalangirira nti chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine ey'enjawulo zaali z'emu ku ddagala ery'okunoonyerezaamu mu kugezesa kwa Solidarity.
Gavana wa New York Andrew Cuomo yalangirira nti okugezesebwa kwa New York kw'eddagala lya chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine kwandibadde kutandika nga 24 Ogwokusatu. Nga 28 Ogwokusatu, FDA yakkiriza okukozesa hydroxychloroquine sulfate ne chloroquine phosphate wansi w'Emergency Use Authorization (EUA).
