Era mu Maaki 2020, Deutsche Telekom yagabana obubaka bw'ekifo ky'essimu obubikoleddwa n'ekitongole kya gavumenti ya Bugirimaani, Robert Koch Institute, okunoonyereza n'okuziyiza okusaasaana kw'akawuka.
Russia yatandikawo tekinologiya w'okumanya ebiso okusobola okuzuula abaamenya amateeka g'okusibibwa mu kkomera.
Omubaka wa Italy ow'ebyobulamu Giulio Gallera yagambye nti yategeezeddwa abavuzi ba ssimu nti "abantu 40% beeyongera okutambula".
Gavumenti ya Bugirimaani ekoze hackathon ya wiiki ya ssaawa 48 ng'abaddeko basenze 42.000.
Era Pulezidenti wa Estonia, Kersti Kaljulaid, yasabye ensi yonna okussaawo enkola ez'enjawulo okulwanyisa okusaasaana kwa coronavirus.
Abantu bayinza okuwulira ennaku olw'okusibibwa mu kaduukulu, okukendeeza ku ntambula, obutali bulungamu obuva ku bujjanjabi oba okutya ekirwadde.
BBC yakwataganya Rory O'Connor ng'agamba nti, "Okwekuumisa mu bantu, ekiwuubaalo, okweraliikirira eby'obulamu, okweraliikirira n'okugwa mu byenfuna kizibu kya maanyi ekireetera abantu obuzibu bw'okulowooza".
Obulwadde buyinza okuba obw'ekyewuunyo nga tebulina bubonero bwonna, nga bufaanana n'obulwadde obulala obusaasaanira obw'omu lubuto ng'obw'omusujja.
Abalwadde abatono batera okuwona mu wiiki bbiri, ate abo abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi oba obw'omutawaana ennyo bayinza okutwala wiiki ssatu okutuuka ku mukaaga okuwona.
Abakazi abali mu lubuto bayinza okuba mu buzibu obw'amaanyi obw'okulumbibwa COVID-19 okusinziira ku bizuuliddwa okuva ku buwuka obulala obufaanana, nga SARS ne MERS, naye ebizuuliddwa ku COVID-19 tebiriiwo. Mu bantu abamu, COVID-19 eyinza okukosa amawuggwe ne kiviirako obulwadde bw'ekibumba.
Mu abo abakoseddwa ennyo, COVID-19 esobola okukulaakulana mangu n'afuuka ekizibu eky'amaanyi eky'okufuna ekizibu eky'okussa (ARDS) ekiviirako okulemererwa okussa, okutawaanyizibwa oba okulemererwa okw'ebitundu by'omubiri ebingi.
Ebizibu ebiva mu COVID-19 bizingiramu obuwuka obuyitibwa sepsis, obuwuka obuyitirira mu mubiri n'okufuna obuzibu mu mutima, mu nzizi ne mu bwongo.
Obuzibu bw'okwekwata, naddala okwongera mu kiseera kya prothrombin, byalagibwa mu 6% ku abo abakwatibwa COVID-19, ate obuzibu bw'emirimu gy'ensigo bwalabikira mu 4% ku bano.
Abantu nga 20-30% abalina COVID-19 balaga ebirungo by'ekibumba ebyennyamidde (transaminases).
Okusinziira ku alipoota y'emu, ekiseera eky'omuggundu wakati w'okufuna obubonero n'okufa kyali ennaku kkumi, nga ttaano ku zo zaali z'okumala mu ddwaliro.
Kyokka, abalwadde abaaggyibwa mu ICU baalina ekiseera eky'ennaku musanvu wakati w'okusibibwa mu ddwaliro n'okufa.
Mu kunoonyereza ku bantu abaakatandikibwawo, ekiseera ekiwanvu okuva ku kulaga obubonero obusooka okutuuka ku kufa kyali ennaku 14, nga obuwanvu bwonna bwali wakati w'ennaku 6 ne 41.
Mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu ekya National Health Commission (NHC) ekya China, abasajja bafiiridde ku 2.8% ate abakazi 1.7%.
Okunoonyereza ku bwongo kulaga nti waliwo obuvune mu mawuggwe obwava mu butoffaali obwava mu bbugwe bw'omubiri obuyitibwa fibromyxoid mu butoffaali bwombi.
Enkyukakyuka z'obutawanyizibwa bw'akawuka zaalabikira mu pneumocytes.
Ekifaananyi ky'ebiwundu kyali kifaanana n'ekigenda mu maaso eky'okufuna ekizibu eky'okussa (ARDS).
Mu 11.8% ku bafudde abaategeezebwa akakiiko k'ebyobulamu aka China, obuvune ku mutima bwalabisibwa olw'ebirungo bya troponin oba okuyimirira kw'omutima.
Okusinziira ku biwandiiko bya March okuva mu Amerika, 89% ku abo abajjanjabibwa mu malwaliro baalina obulwadde obwaliwo. Okuba nti waliwo obujjanjabi n'enkulaakulana y'ebyenfuna mu kitundu nakyo kiyinza okukosa abafa.
Okulowooza ku kufa olw'obulwadde buno kwawukana olw'enjawulo eziri mu bitundu ebyo, naye era olw'obuvunaanyizibwa bw'enkola.
Okubala abantu abatalina buzibu kiviirako omuwendo gw'abantu abafa okuwera.
Kyokka, eky'okuba nti okufa kuva ku mbeera ezaaliwo mu biseera ebyayita kiyinza okutegeeza nti omuwendo gw'abafa mu kiseera kino tegutwalibwa ng'ekintu ekikulu.
Abanywa ssigala baakubeera ababiri n'okusatu nga balina obubonero obw'amaanyi bwa COVID-19 era nga baakubirwa emirundi 2.4 nga beetaaga okujjanjabibwa ennyo oba okufa nga bakwatagana n'abo abatanywa ssigala. Okweraliikirira kuddiridde ku ngeri obulwadde buno gye buyinza okwongera okubalukawo.
Ekitongole kya Hong Kong Hospital Authority kyazuula nti abantu abamu abawona obulwadde buno, obuwumbi bw'amawuggwe bwawanvuwa okuva ku 20% okutuuka ku 30%, era ebifaananyi by'amawuggwe biraga nti ebitundu by'omubiri byayonoonebwa.
Kino kiyinza n'okutuusa ku bulwadde bw'okulabirirwa oluvannyuma lw'okuwona.
Mu March 2020, kyali tekimanyiddwa oba nga obulwadde obwayita bukola obwa nnamaddala era obumalawo obulwadde mu bantu abawona obulwadde.
Obulwadde butwalibwa ng'obusobola okuva ku bulwadde buno, okusinziira ku nneeyisa ya ssennyiga corona endala, naye waliwo abantu abazuuliddwa nga bawonye COVID-19 nga bafunye obubonero obutuufu ku coronavirus oluvannyuma.
Embeera zino zikkirizibwa okuba nga zeeyongedde okwonooneka olw'obulwadde obumaze ebbanga nga bubeerawo so si okudda mu mbeera.
Ekirwadde kino kitwalibwa okuba nga kya butonde era nga kiva mu nsolo, nga kiva mu bulwadde obugenda buva mu bantu.
Ensibuko yennyini temanyiddwa, naye mu December 2019 okusaasaana kw'obulwadde kwali kumpi mu bujjuvu nga kusindikibwa okuva ku muntu okudda ku muntu.
Okunoonyereza ku bantu 41 abaasooka okukakasibwa nti balina COVID-19, okwafulumizibwa mu Jjanwali 2020 mu The Lancet, kwalaga nti obulwadde buno bwabalukawo nga 1 December 2019.
Ebitabo ebitegekeddwa okuva mu WHO byalangirira ku ntandikwa y'obubonero nga 8 December 2019.
Ebintu ebiwerako bikozesebwa okutunula okufa.
Enamba zino za njawulo okusinziira ku kitundu n'ebiseera era zikubirizibwa omuwendo gw'okugezesebwa, omutindo gw'enteekateeka y'ebyobulamu, enkola y'obujjanjabi, ekiseera ekiyiseewo okuva ku ntandikwa y'okusaasaana kw'obulwadde n'engeri z'abantu gamba ng'emyaka, ekikula n'embeera y'obulamu.
Mu nkomerero ya 2019, WHO yawa ICD-10 obulwadde obw'amangu U07.1 olw'abafa olw'obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 obwakakasibwa mu lab ate U07.2 olw'abafa olw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obwakakasibwa mu lab nga tebuliko bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2.Eky'omuwendo gw'abafa ku balwadde gwe muwendo gw'abafa nga bagabiddwa ku muwendo gw'abalwadde abazuuliddwa mu kiseera ekimu.
Okusinziira ku bibalo bya Yunivasite ya Johns Hopkins, omuwendo gw'abantu abafa mu nsi yonna gwe 6.9% (153,822/2,240,191) nga 17 Apuli 2020.
Omuwendo guno gwawukana okusinziira ku kitundu. Enkola endala z'ezo ezirimu omuwendo gw'abantu abafa (CFR), nga kino kiraga omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa nga bafiira mu bulwadde, n'omuwendo gw'abantu abafa nga bafunye obulwadde (IFR), nga kino kiraga omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa (abazuuliddwa n'abatazuuliddwa) abafa olw'obulwadde.
Ebiri mu biwandiiko bino tebikwatagana na kiseera era bigoberera abantu ab'enjawulo okuva ku bulwadde okutuuka ku buzibu.
Wadde nga si buli muntu akwatibwa obulwadde bw'obulwadde nti afuna obuwuka obwo, obuwuka obwo busobola okuwa obubaka ku bantu bameka abakwatiddwa obulwadde.
Mu kifo ekikulu omwali ekirwadde kino mu Italy, Castiglione d'Adda, ekyalo ekitonotono eky'abantu 4600, 80 (1.7%) bafudde dda.
Mu Gangelt, ekirwadde kyasaasaana ku mikolo gya Carnival, era ne kisaasaana ku bato, ne kiviirako okufa okuwera, era si bonna abafudde COVID-19 be baateekebwa mu nkola mu ngeri eyo.
Ate era, enteekateeka y'ebyobulamu mu Bugirimaani teyeekubye nnyo.
Mu Netherlands, abantu nga 3% bayinza okuba n'ebiwuka eby'omubiri, nga bwe bavumirirwa okuva mu bantu abagaba omusaayi.
Abantu 69 (0.004% ku bantu) bakakasibwa okuba nga baafa COVID-19.
Obuzibu bw'ekirwadde kino n'omuwendo gw'abafa gwa njawulo ku basajja n'abakazi.
Okufa kwa basinga ku basajja mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu China ne Italy.
Akabi akali mu basajja kabaawo nga baweza emyaka 50, ng'enjogera wakati w'abasajja n'abakazi esemberera ku myaka 90.
Mu China, omuwendo gw'abasajja abafa gwali 2.8 ku buli 100 ate ogw'abakazi gwali 1.7 ku buli 100.
Ensonga eziviirako enjawulo mu by'obuseegu tezimanyiddwa, naye obuzaale n'empisa biyinza okuba nga bye bimu ku biviirako enjawulo eno.
Enjawulo mu bujjanjabi bw'omubiri okusinziira ku buli kikula, obuwuka obutonnya obunywa ssigala mu bakazi n'abasajja abafuna endwadde ez'enjawulo nga bwa puleesa nga bakyali bato okusinga abakazi, biyinza okuba nga bye byaviirako okufa okw'amaanyi mu basajja.
Mu Bulaaya, 57% ku bakwatibwa baali basajja ate 72% ku baafa COVID-19 baali basajja.
Okuva mu Apuli 2020, gavumenti ya Amerika tegyafaayo ku biwandiiko ebikwata ku kwetaba mu bantu abalina obulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Okunoonyereza kulaga nti endwadde z'akawuka nga Ebola, HIV, omusujja ne SARS zikosa abasajja n'abakazi mu ngeri ya njawulo.
Omusingi omunene ogw'abakozi b'ebyobulamu, naddala abajjanjabi, bakazi, era balina omukisa omunene ogw'okutuukibwako akawuka.
Ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu kyalangirira nga 11 February 2020 nti erinnya ly'obulwadde erya bulijjo lyali "COVID-19".
Akulira WHO Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yannyonnyola nti CO etegeeza corona, VI eriva ku virus, D eriva ku bulwadde, ate 19 kwe kuba ddi obulwadde bwe bwazuulibwa: 31 December 2019.
Erinnya lino lyalondebwa okwewala okutegeeza ekifo ekimu eky'ettaka (ng'ekyokulabirako, China), ensolo oba ekibinja ky'abantu, nga kituukana n'okuteesa okw'ensi yonna okw'okuyita amannya okutumbula abantu. Obutabanguko obuleeta COVID-19 buyitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
WHO era ekozesa "akawuka ka COVID-19" ne "akawuka akaleeta COVID-19" mu kwogeraganya mu bantu.
Obulwadde ne akawuka ka bulijjo biyitibwa "kokoonavairusi".
Mu kiseera eky'okusaasaana kw'obulwadde mu Wuhan, China, akawuka n'obulwadde byayogerwako nga "coronavirus" ne "Wuhan coronavirus".
Mu Jjanwali 2020, WHO yakubiriza 2019-nCov ne 2019-nCoV ekirwadde eky'amaanyi eky'okussa omukka ng'amannya ag'ebbanga ag'akawuka n'obulwadde okusinziira ku bulagirizi obwa 2015 obugaana okukozesa ebifo mu mannya g'obulwadde n'obubulwadde.
Amannya ag'obwannannyini COVID-19 ne SARS-CoV-2 gaafulumizibwa nga 11 February 2020.
Olw'obutakkiriza bwa maanyi mu nsalo z'ebikozesebwa, abakola ebintu ebimu eby'ekinnansi bafulumya ebintu eby'ebyobulamu nga ssabbuuni w'ennyindo n'ebitundu eby'omugaali gw'obusawo.
Mu kyokulabirako kimu, eddwaliro mu Italy bwe lyali lyetaaga amasavu g'omuwaabi w'ebyafaayo, era nga n'omuwaabi tasobola kugaba mu budde obwetaagisa, ekitongole ekiggya mu kitundu kino kyakola enkola y'obukodyo obw'ekikugu ne kifulumya amasavu 100 ge kyetaaga mu kiro kimu.
Oluvannyuma lw'okusaasaana kw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19, endowooza z'obulabe, obubaka obutali butuufu n'obw'obulimba byajjawo ku nsibuko, omutindo, okutangira, obujjanjabi n'ebirala ebikwata ku kirwadde kino era ne bicaaka nnyo ku mutimbagano.
Abantu kirabika basobola okusaasaanya akawuka kano ku nsolo endala.
Okunoonyereza kuno kwalemwa okuzuula obujulizi obulaga nti akawuka kano kaakula mu mbizzi, amanda ne enkoko.
Tewali ddagala oba ddagala erikkirizibwa okujjanjaba ekirwadde kino.
Okunoonyereza okw'ensi yonna ku ddagala n'eddagala mu COVID-19 kugenda mu maaso nga kukolebwa ebitongole bya gavumenti, ebibiina by'abasomesa n'abanoonyereza ku by'emikono.
Mu March, ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu kyatandikawo "Okukebera kwa Ssolidary" okusalawo ku bujjanjabi bw'eddagala eririmu eddagala erirwanyisa obuwuka eririna obusobozi obw'okutuuka ku buwanguzi.
Tewali ddagala lya bulwadde, naye ebitongole eby'enjawulo bikola ddagala ly'eddagala erigema.
Omulimu ogwakolebwa ku SARS-CoV mu kusooka gukozesebwa kubanga SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikozesa ACE2 okuyingira mu butoffaali bw'omuntu.
Waliwo enkola z'okukoza enzijanjaba ssatu ezinoonyerezaako.
Okusooka, abakugu banoonya okuzimba eddagala ly'akawuka.
Okukozesa akawuka ako, ka kube nga tekakoze oba nga kafudde, kigendererwa kya kukakasa nti omubiri gw'omuntu gufuna obujjanjabi obw'amangu obw'obutagasa ku bulwadde obupya obuva ku COVID-19.
Enteekateeka ey'okubiri, eddagala ly'obukuumi erya subunit, erina ekigendererwa eky'okuteekawo eddagala erisobozesa obukuumi bw'omubiri okuziyiza obumu ku butundu obumu obw'akawuka.
Ku SARS-CoV-2, okunoonyereza ng'okwo kwesigama ku buwungezi bwa S-spike obuyamba akawuka okuyingira mu ACE2 enzyme receptor.
Enteekateeka ey'okusatu y'ey'eddagala ly'omubiri erya nucleic acid (eddagala lya DNA oba RNA, enkola empya ey'okuteeka eddagala ly'omubiri).
Abalwadde b'ekirwadde okuva mu buli emu ku ntekateeka zino balina okugezesebwa okulaba oba ba ddembe oba tebabi. Nga 16 Ogwokusatu 2020, okusooka okunoonyereza ku bulwadde bw'ekirwadde kwatandika nga kw'abako abakola ku bwetaavu bana mu Seattle.
Omukutu gulimu code y'ekika kya DNA etali ya bulabe eyakolebwa okuva ku kawuka akaleeta obulwadde. Okweyongera okw'obutonde bw'omubiri okwekubidde ku antibodi kwalagulwa ng'ekisobola okuleetawo eddagala erigema SARS-COV-2, naye kino ky'ekikontana.
Mu April 2020 waliwo okunoonyereza okw'emirundi esatu okukolebwa ku bantu.
Okugezesebwa musanvu kwali kwekenneenya obujjanjabi obwaweebwa eddagala ku ndwadde ya siriimu, nga kw'otadde n'okuyiga kwa hydroxychloroquine oba chloroquine.
Eddagala erirwanyisa obuwuka likola okunoonyereza kw'Abakiina, nga n'ebirungo mwenda eby'okugezesa okw'ekigero III ku remdesivir mu nsi ez'enjawulo byalina okutegeezebwa ku nkomerero ya April.
Okwejjukanya okw'amaanyi okw'okukulaakulanya eddagala ly'okwekebejja COVID-19 n'eddagala eririko gw'osobola okwekebera, kwaliwo mu Apuli 2020. Emiti egiziyiza ekirwadde egiwerako egiba egiriwo gibalibwa mu nkola ey'okujjanjaba COVID-19, omuli remdesivir, chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir ne lopinavir/ritonavir nga gikozeseddwa ne interferon beta.
Waliwo obujulizi obusookerwako ku buwanguzi bwa remdesivir, okuva mu Maaki 2020.
Okwewala okulongooka kwalabikamu mu balwadde abajjanjabwa remdesivir ey'okusaasira.
Ebigezo by'eddagala eby'omutendera III bikolebwa mu Amerika, China ne Italy. Chloroquine, eddaako okusaalirwa endwadde ya malwadde, yasomebwa mu China mu February 2020, n'ebyava mu kusooka.
Kyokka waliwo abaagala okunoonyereza kuno kuddamu okukolebweko.
Abakungu b'ebyobulamu mu Korea ne China bakubiriza okukozesa chloroquine.
Kyokka, Wuhan Institute of Virology, wadde nga ekubiriza eddagala lya ligramu emu olunaku, egamba nti eddagala eryo emirundi ebiri lya kabi nnyo era liyinza okuba ery'obulabe.
Nga 28 Maaki 2020, FDA yakkiriza okukozesa eddagala lya hydroxychloroquine ne chloroquine mu bwangu nga abasawo abalwanyisa abantu abalina COVID-19 bwe basalawo. Amagezi agava mu China aga 7th edition era gazingiramu ne interferon, ribavirin oba umifenovir nga bikozesebwa okulwanyisa COVID-19.
Ebiriwo biraga nti eddagala lya ribavirin lyetaagisa nnyo okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu mubiri.
Nitazoxanide yakubirizibwa okwongera okunoonyereza mu vivo oluvannyuma lw'okulaga nti eremeddeko erya wansi liziyiza SARS-CoV-2. Okunoonyereza kulaga nti okunoonyereza ku protein ey'ekigero okusooka okuyita mu transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) kukulu nnyo eri SARS-CoV-2 okuyita mu kukwatagana n'omutegeeza ACE2.
Okunoonyereza ku chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine nga kuliko oba nga tolina azithromycin kukwatiddwa nnyo ebiremesezza abasawo okukkiriza enzijanjaba zino awatali kuyiga mu maaso. Oseltamivir tekiremesa SARS-CoV-2 mu vitro era tekimanyiddwaako mu kujjanjaba COVID-19.
Ekirevu kya cytokine kiyinza okuba ekizibu mu mitendera egy'oluvannyuma mu COVID-19 ey'amaanyi.
Waliwo obujulizi obulaga nti hydroxychloroquine eyinza okuba n'ebikolwa ebirwanyisa omuzikiza gw'ebitundu by'omubiri ebiyitibwa cytokine. Tocilizumab yayingizibwa mu mitendera gy'obujjanjabi mu China National Health Commission oluvannyuma lw'okumaliriza okunoonyereza okutono.
Kigezesebwa mu kigezo ekitali kya buwumbi mu mitendera 2 ku mutendera gw'eggwanga mu Italy oluvannyuma lw'okulaba ebivaamu mu bantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Nga kikwatagana n'okugezesa omusaayi okwa seramu ferritin okuzuula ebise by'ekika kya cytokine, kigendereddwa okuziyiza ebintu ng'ebyo, ebirowoozebwa okuba ensonga y'okufa mu bantu abamu abakwatibwako.
Interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yakkirizibwa FDA okusinziira ku kunoonyereza kwa mirundi ebiri okukolebwa ku bujjanjabi bw'endwadde eya steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome eyaleetebwa ensonga endala, okujjanjabibwa kw'amasimu g'omulembe aga CAR T cell, mu 2017.
Okutuusa kati, tewali bukakafu bwa mukolo, obulagiddwa nti tocilizumab y'eddagala erisobola okujjanjaba CRS.
Okusaasaanya antibodies ezirongooseddwa era ezirongoosebwa ezikolebwa obusimu bw'omubiri bw'abo abawonye COVID-19 eri abantu ababyetaaga okunoonyerezebwako ng'enkola y'obutaba na ddagala lya ddagala erigema.
Enteekateeka eno yagezesebwa ku SARS nga teyavaamu bibala.
Okuziyiza akawuka ke nkola ey'okukola nga eddagala ery'omubiri ogutawaanya liyinza okutabangula okulwanyisa SARS-CoV-2.
Kyokka, enkola endala, nga antibody-dependent cellular cytotoxicity ne/oba phagocytosis, ziyinza okuba nga zikola.
Enkola endala ez'obujjanjabi obw'emirambo egirwanyisa endwadde, gamba ng'okukozesa eddagala erirwanyisa endwadde erya monoclonal, likola.
Okukola serumu ey'abalwadde abawonye, erimu ekitundu ky'omusaayi oguli mu butto okuva ku balwadde abawonye era nga kirimu obuwuka obuziyiza akawuka kano, kiyinza okwongerwako okusobola okusaasaanya amangu.
Obulwadde bwa Coronaviruses, ekibinja ky'obulwadde obufaanagana
Li Wenliang, omusawo mu ddwaliro lya Central Hospital e Wuhan, oluvannyuma eyafuna COVID-19 n'afa oluvannyuma lw'okulangirira okusaasaanya akawuka.
